==Entrances & Exits==
===Entrances===
*Holding anything perceived as 'cute' upon entering a new level has a slight possibility of being transported to '''Level 974''' instead of the intended location.
*Achieving liberation from [https://backrooms-wiki.wikidot.com/ super-ultra-omega hell] paves the path to [https://backrooms.fandom.com/ mildly okay hell], bringing wanderers here.
===Exits===
*The only known exit is by antagonizing '''Kitty''', resulting in a violent attack that eventually teleport wanderers to [[Level 630]].

